  <brief_title>Prediction Value of the BreathID 13C-Methacetin Breath Test for Hepatic Decompensation</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Prediction Value of the BreathID 13C-Methacetin Breath Test for Hepatic Decompensation; a Retrospective Analysis</official_title>
  <sponsors>
    <lead_sponsor>
      <agency>Exalenz Bioscience LTD.</agency>
